Package: f1dataR
Title: F1 Data in R
Version: 0.3.7
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Santiago",
           family = "Casanova",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "santiago.casanova@yahoo.com")
Description: A collection of funtions that wrap Ergast API Formula 1 data and F1 offial data via the fastf1 python library. The load_* function family allow the user to get a neat dataframe of the requested data.
Config/reticulate:
  list(
    packages = list(
      list(package = "fastf1", pip = TRUE)
    )
  )
